{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_03_03",
  "title": "サニーピース 03 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "学校でいじめられてたことを\n周りの人に相談しなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn't talk to anyone\nabout being bullied at school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.9029477119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.2333334922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "した……親に話したら、お父さんが学校に相談して……\n担任の先生が、クラスのみんなに注意することになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did… I told my parents‚ and my dad talked to the school…\nSo the homeroom teacher had to warn everyone in my class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2333334922,
      "endTime": 17.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.6499300001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "それで先生は……帰りのHRで\n私をみんなの前に立たせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ during homeroom at the end of the day‚\nhe made me stand in front of everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6499300001,
      "endTime": 24.4832633015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "「兵藤はみんなにいじめられていると言ってる\nみんな、兵藤とちゃんと仲良くしろ」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Hyodo says she's being bullied by everyone‚\nso everyone‚ make sure to get along with Hyodo.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6832629201,
      "endTime": 32.890043639699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.1567089077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "それから私に「いじめはいじめられる側にも原因がある\nお前もみんなと打ち解けるように努力しろ」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then he told me‚ \"There's a reason why people get bullied.\nYou should make an effort to get along with everyone too.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1567089077,
      "endTime": 44.536276944200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6900356288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-mone009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの酷いよ！\n雫ちゃんは何も悪いことしてないのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's terrible!\nShizuku-chan didn't do anything wrong!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6900356288,
      "endTime": 50.8926659579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.0900356288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、いじめは収まったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ did the bullying stop?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0900356288,
      "endTime": 54.523365020300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7233646388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "収まるどころか……どんどんエスカレートした……\n毎日持ち物がなくなって……酷い言葉も沢山言われた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It didn't stop at all… It just escalated…\nMy belongings would disappear every day… and they said so many cruel things to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7233646388,
      "endTime": 64.8266641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.0922733779
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの視線や、話し声が気になって……\n教室にいるだけで、気分が悪くなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so conscious of their gazes and whispers…\nJust being in the classroom made me feel sick…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0922733779,
      "endTime": 73.823769998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "休み時間になると、保健室に逃げて……\nお昼はトイレでお弁当を食べたりして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd run to the nurse's office during breaks…\nI'd eat my lunch in the bathroom…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0237696166,
      "endTime": 81.88166098549999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.081660604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんはずっと一人で頑張ってたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You went through all that alone‚ Shizuku-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.081660604,
      "endTime": 86.43316760050001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.7816590782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "結局、学校には行かなくなった……家に引きこもって\n毎日、アイドルのDVDを見るようになった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ I stopped going to school… I stayed at home‚\nwatching idol DVDs all day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7816590782,
      "endTime": 97.2000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3316584583
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3316584583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "（それからしばらくして、私を心配したお姉ちゃんが）\n（様子を見に来てくれた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（A while later‚ my sister came to check on me because she was worried…）\n（so she came to see me…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3816584583,
      "endTime": 106.0453774448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おばさんから話は聞いたよ。最近仕事が忙しくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from your aunt. I'm sorry I haven't been able to be there for you‚ Shizuku‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2453770633,
      "endTime": 112.11204373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "雫が大変な時に、そばにいてあげられなくてごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't been able to be there for you when you were going through a tough time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.11204373,
      "endTime": 116.6187084194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8120416954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは悪くない……むしろ、私はいつも\nお姉ちゃんに助けられてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not your fault… Actually‚ you've always\nbeen there for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8120416954,
      "endTime": 123.8543546036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.1876855209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "推しが、ステージから笑いかけてくれるから……\n辛い時でも……頑張って生きていこうって思えた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My oshi smiles at me from the stage…\nSo even when things are tough… I can keep going…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1876855209,
      "endTime": 132.4997714355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが……アイドルがいなかったら……\nきっと、私……耐えられなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it weren't for you… if it weren't for idols…\nI probably wouldn't have been able to make it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7997771575,
      "endTime": 140.81843941949998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.018439038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "でも……これって現実逃避してるだけ……？\nアイドルが心の支えって、変なのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… is this just me running away from reality…?\nIs it strange to have an idol as your emotional support…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.018439038,
      "endTime": 150.57967236780001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "変じゃないよ。大好きな人がいて、その人を想うと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not strange. It's a wonderful thing to have someone you love‚ someone who",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7796719863,
      "endTime": 156.0130073542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "元気になれるのは、とっても素敵なことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "makes you feel better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0130073542,
      "endTime": 159.4663559271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.6796892796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね……アイドルを好きなのは\nバカにされるようなことじゃないよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right… Liking idols\nisn't something to be ashamed of…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.6796892796,
      "endTime": 166.01352135279998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになりたいって思うのは……\n悪いことじゃないよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wanting to be an idol…\nisn't wrong…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.2135209713,
      "endTime": 171.2665186562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.5661283169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "悪い訳ないでしょ。雫はやりたいことをやっていいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it's not wrong. You can do whatever you want‚ Shizuku‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.5661283169,
      "endTime": 176.5327919318,
