      "text": "その後、お父さんの転勤で星見市に引っ越して……\n私は、誰も私のことを知らない高校に通い始めた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ we moved to Hoshimi City because of my dad's transfer…\nAnd I started going to a high school where no one knew me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.7357334447,
      "endTime": 264.7709486318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
